4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with essential technologies such as JavaScript and Python. The program spans over 18 weeks with three classes per week, ensuring a hands-on learning experience with a low student-to-teacher ratio (1:7). Students will engage in algorithm scripting, utilize APIs, and ultimately develop a personal project, gaining valuable experience. No prior coding skills are necessary, and the curriculum is available in both English and Spanish. Participants are awarded a Full-Stack Developer certificate upon completion. More details can be found at [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop